OL,3,CTeenager arrested in connection to
OL,4,CHuddersfield shooting
OL,6,FA 19-year-old from Huddersfield has
OL,7,Fbeen arrested in connection with a
OL,8,Fshooting in Birkby on Wednesday, 8
OL,9,FApril.
OL,11,FThe suspect was taken into custody
OL,12,Flast night (Tuesday 14 April) after a
OL,13,F17-year-old victim suffered a non-life-
OL,14,Fthreatening leg injury.
OL,16,FHe remains in police custody on
OL,17,Fsuspicion of attempted murder and
OL,18,Fpossession of a firearm with intent to
OL,19,Fendanger life.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
