OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1776269465
OL,3,CTeenager arrested in connection to
OL,4,CHuddersfield shooting
OL,6,FThe Homicide and Major Enquiry Team,
OL,7,Fwhich is investigating the incident on
OL,8,Fa football pitch off Spaines Road in
OL,9,FBirkby, said they are actively
OL,10,Fpursuing multiple lines of enquiry.
OL,12,FPolice have established that the
OL,13,Fvictim was walking with friends along
OL,14,Fa woodland path away from the football
OL,15,Fpitch between 8:30 pm and 9:00 pm when
OL,16,Fa suspected firearm was discharged.
OL,17,FJust prior to the shooting, two masked
OL,18,Fmen were spotted behind trees in a
OL,19,Fsnicket off Richmond Avenue.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
